No flavor.
The mac n cheese was like a creamy soup and they were small shells.
I got the waffle fries and they were lame.
Best thing I had was the biscuit they include with every meal (I guess).
Over all I would put this as the worst BBQ restaurant I have had in all of Vegas.
Its near K's BBQ which I used to drive all the way across town for.
Between these 2 restaurants you have a good representation of how you can F up BBQ.
Avoid this place.

